    "name": "section-services-hero",
    "content": "<!-- AI-IMAGE: services-hero-bg | Services page hero. Treatment room or clinical setting that signals modern care.\n       SEARCH KEYWORDS: dental treatment room, modern dental chair, clinical operatory, treatment area wide shot.\n       REQUIREMENTS: Landscape, minimum 1920x1080, professional quality.\n       FALLBACK: Any modern dental operatory or clinical setting photo.\n       INSTRUCTION: Replace ONLY the url() value inside the section's background-image style; keep the linear-gradient overlay intact. Do not render this as an <img> element. -->\n<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero relative w-full min-h-[560px] md:min-h-[680px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-24 bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat text-ivory\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,23,42,0.75), rgba(15,23,42,0.55), rgba(15,23,42,0.85)), url('https://picsum.photos/1920/1080?random=50');\">\n  \n  <div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 text-center flex flex-col items-center\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-eyebrow | Replace with \"Our Services\" or similar. -->\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans text-white/60\">Our Services</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-heading | Replace with a compelling services heading.\n         Use <span class=\"text-accent\"> for accent color on key phrase. -->\n    <h1 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-heading font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white font-medium leading-[1.1] mb-6\">\n      Comprehensive dental care <span class=\"text-accent\">built around you</span>\n    </h1>\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-subtext | Replace with a description of the practice's service breadth. -->\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-subtext text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl font-sans text-white/90\">\n      From routine cleanings to advanced restorative work, our team delivers expert care with a gentle touch. Every treatment plan is tailored to your unique needs and goals.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-16\">\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-cta-primary | Replace href and text if needed. -->\n\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n\n      <a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-cta-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-90 font-sans\">\n        Request a Consultation\n      </a>\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-cta-secondary | Replace href and phone number. -->\n      <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-cta-secondary inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-80 font-sans border border-white/30\">\n        <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 8V5z\"/></svg>\n        Call Us Today\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 w-full max-w-3xl\">\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-stat-1 | Replace number and label. -->\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-stat-1 rounded-2xl px-4 py-4 flex flex-col items-center gap-1 bg-white/10\">\n        <span class=\"font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white\">10+</span>\n        <span class=\"text-xs font-sans text-center leading-snug text-white/70\">Services offered</span>\n      </div>\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-stat-2 | Replace number and label. -->\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-stat-2 rounded-2xl px-4 py-4 flex flex-col items-center gap-1 bg-white/10\">\n        <span class=\"font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white\">15+</span>\n        <span class=\"text-xs font-sans text-center leading-snug text-white/70\">Years of experience</span>\n      </div>\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-stat-3 | Replace number and label. -->\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-stat-3 rounded-2xl px-4 py-4 flex flex-col items-center gap-1 bg-white/10\">\n        <span class=\"font-serif text-2xl font-semibold text-white\">5-Star</span>\n        <span class=\"text-xs font-sans text-center leading-snug text-white/70\">Rated practice</span>\n      </div>\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-hero-stat-4 | Replace number and label. -->\n      <div class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-hero-component-stat-4 rounded-2xl px-4 py-5 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1 bg-white/20\">\n        <span class=\"font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-white\">Same-Day</span>\n        <span class=\"text-xs font-sans text-center leading-snug text-white/90\">emergencies</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
