    "content": "<section class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-cta py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-gradient-brand text-ivory\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\">\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-cta-eyebrow | Replace with a short label. -->\n      <span class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-cta-component-eyebrow text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase font-sans text-gray-500\">Your Next Step</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-cta-heading | Replace with an inviting CTA heading. -->\n    <h2 class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-cta-component-heading font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white leading-tight mb-5\">\n      Not sure which service you need? <span class=\"text-primary\">We can help.</span>\n    </h2>\n    <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-cta-subtext | Replace with a reassuring paragraph. -->\n    <p class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-cta-component-subtext text-white/80 font-sans text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10\">\n      Our team will evaluate your needs, explain your options clearly, and walk you through every step of your treatment plan. No pressure, no surprises.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\">\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-cta-primary | Replace href and text if needed. -->\n\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: cta-label | Choose label by business.category:\n       - Endodontist / Endodontics → \"Book Appointment\"\n       - Orthodontist / Orthodontics → \"Schedule a Consultation\"\n       - Default / other dental → \"Request a Consultation\"\n       Apply the same label consistently across header, body, and footer CTAs for this site. -->\n\n      <a href=\"/consultation\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-cta-component-cta-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-opacity hover:opacity-90 font-sans\">\n        Request a Consultation\n      </a>\n      <!-- AI-CONTENT: services-cta-secondary | Replace href and text if needed. -->\n      <a href=\"/services\" class=\"alloro-tpl-v1-release-section-services-cta-component-cta-secondary inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border border-gray-300 text-white/80 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-colors hover:border-primary hover:text-primary font-sans\">\n        View All Services\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
